"jumps break at camel case humps."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autocenter cursor:"
msgstr "Kursori automaatne tsentreerimine:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the number of lines to maintain visible above and below the cursor when "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Määrab ridade arvu, mida võimaluse korral näidatakse all- ja ülevalpool "
"kursorit."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Selection Mode"
msgstr "Tekstivaliku režiim"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "Normaalne"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selections will be overwritten by typed text and will be lost on cursor "
"movement."
msgstr ""
"Valik kirjutatakse teksti sisestamisel üle ja läheb kaotsi kursori "
"liikumisel."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "Persistent"
msgstr "Püsiv"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selections will stay even after cursor movement and typing."
msgstr "Valik jääb alles ka pärast kursori liikumist ja teksti sisestamist."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow scrolling past the end of the document"
msgstr "Kerimise lubamine üle dokumendi lõpu"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you scroll past the end of the document. This can be used "
"to vertically centre the bottom of the document, or put it on top of the "
"current view."
msgstr ""
"See võimaldab kerida üle dokumendi lõpu. Seda saab kasutada näiteks "
"dokumendi allosa püstiseks tsentreerimiseks või selle paigutamiseks aktiivse "
"vaate ülaossa."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backspace key removes character’s base with its diacritics"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selected, composed characters are removed with their diacritics instead "
"of only removing the base character. This is useful for Indic locales."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multicursor modifier"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you set the modifier that will be used to create multiple "
"cursors with &LMB; click. You need to press the modifiers and click &LMB; to "
"create a cursor at the desired location. See <link linkend=\"kate-part-"
"create-multiple-cursors\">Creating multiple cursors</link> to discover other "
"ways to create multiple cursors."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation"
msgstr "Treppimine"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default indentation mode:"
msgstr "Treppimise vaikerežiim:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the automatic indentation mode you want to use as default. It is "
"strongly recommended to use <userinput>None</userinput> or "
"<userinput>Normal</userinput> here, and use filetype configurations to set "
"other indentation modes for text formats like C/C++ code or &XML;."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab valida vaikimisi kasutatava automaatse treppimise režiimi. Väga "
"soovitav on valida siin <userinput>Puudub</userinput> või "
"<userinput>Tavaline</userinput> ning määrata failitüübi seadistustes "
"treppimise režiimid erijuhtudeks, näiteks C/C++ koodile või &XML;-ile."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indent using"
msgstr "Treppimisel kasutatakse"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabulators"
msgstr "Tabeldusmärgid"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled the editor will insert tabulator characters when you "
"press the &Tab; key or use <link linkend=\"kate-part-autoindent\">automatic "
"indentation</link>."
msgstr ""
"Märkimise korral lisab redaktor tabeldusmärgid, kui vajutad klahvi &Tab; või "
"kasutad <link linkend=\"kate-part-autoindent\">automaatset treppimist</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spaces"
msgstr "Tühikud"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled the editor will insert a calculated number of spaces "
"according to the position in the text and the <option>tab-width</option> "
"setting when you press the &Tab; key or use <link linkend=\"kate-part-"
"autoindent\">automatic indentation</link>."
msgstr ""
"Märkimise korral lisab redaktor klahvi &Tab; vajutamisel või <link linkend="
"\"kate-part-autoindent\">automaatse treppimise</link> kasutamisel kindla "
"arvu tühikuid vastavalt asukohale tekstis ja määratlusele <option>TAB laius</"
"option>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabulators and Spaces"
msgstr "Tabeldusmärgid ja tühikud"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled, the editor will insert spaces as describe above when "
"indenting or pressing &Tab; at the beginning of a line, but insert "
"tabulators when the &Tab; key is pressed in the middle or end of a line."
msgstr ""
"Märkimise korral lisab redaktor treppimise või klahvi &Tab; vajutamise "
"korral rea algusse tühikud, kuid samas lisab tabeldusmärgid, kui klahvi "
"&Tab; vajutada rea keskel või lõpus viibides."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tab width:"
msgstr "TAB laius:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This configures the number of spaces that are displayed in place of a "
"tabulator character."
msgstr "See määrab tühikute arvu, mida näidatakse tabeldusmärgi asemel."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation width:"
msgstr "Treppimise laius:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The indentation width is the number of spaces which is used to indent a "
"line. If configured to indent using tabulators, a tabulator character is "
"inserted if the indentation is divisible by the tab width."
msgstr ""
"Treppimise laius tänendab tühikute arvu, mida kasutatakse reale taande "
"andmiseks. Kui treppimine käib tabeldusmärkidega. lisatakse tabeldusmärk, "
"kui taane on jagatav tabulaatori laiusega."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation Properties"
msgstr "Treppimise omadused"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep extra spaces"
msgstr "Liigsed tühikud hoitakse alles"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is disabled, changing the indentation level aligns a line to "
"a multiple of the width specified in <guilabel>Indentation width</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Kui see on märkimata, joondab treppimise taseme muutmine rea valikuga "
"<guilabel>Treppimise laius</guilabel> määratud laiuse kordse võrra."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adjust indentation of text pasted from the clipboard"
msgstr "Lõikepuhvrist asetatud teksti korral kohandatakse treppimist"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, text pasted from the clipboard is indented. "
"Triggering the <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem> action removes the "
"indentation."
msgstr ""
"Selle märkimisel trepitakse lõikepuhvrist asetatud tekst. Menüükäsuga "
"<guimenuitem>Võta tagasi</guimenuitem> saab treppimise eemaldada."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation Actions"
msgstr "Treppimistoimingud"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backspace key in leading blank space unindents"
msgstr "Backspace rida alustavas tühjas ruumis vähendab treppimist"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Backspace; key decreases the indentation "
"level if the cursor is located in the leading blank space of a line."
msgstr ""
"Sisselülitamisel saab klahviga &Backspace; vähendada taanet, kui kursor asub "
"rida alustavas tühjas ruumis."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tab key action (if no selection exists)"
msgstr "Tabeldusklahvi toiming (kui valik puudub)"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:631
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you want &Tab; to align the current line in the current code block "
#| "like in emacs, make &Tab; a shortcut to the action <guimenuitem>Align</"
#| "guimenuitem>."
msgid ""
"If you want &Tab; to align the current line in the current code block like "
"in &Emacs;, make &Tab; a shortcut to the action <guimenuitem>Format "
"Indentation</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid, et &Tab; joondaks aktiivse rea aktiivses koodiblokis nagu "
"Emacsis, muuda &Tab; toimingu <guimenuitem>Joonda</guimenuitem> kiirklahviks."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always advance to the next tab position"
msgstr "Alati siirdutakse järgmisele tabelduskohale"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Tab; key always inserts white space so that "
"the next tab position is reached. If the option <guilabel>Insert spaces "
"instead of tabulators</guilabel> on the <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab in "
"the <guilabel>Editing</guilabel> page is enabled, spaces are inserted; "
"otherwise, a single tabulator is inserted."
msgstr ""
"Sisselülitamisel lisab klahv &Tab; alati tühja ruumi, et jõuda järgmisele "
"tabelduskohale. Kui lehekülje <guilabel>Redigeerimine</guilabel> kaardil "
"<guilabel>Üldine</guilabel> on märgitud valik <guilabel>Tabeldusmärgid "
"asendatakse tühikutega</guilabel>, lisatakse tühikud, vastasel juhul üks "
"tabeldusmärk."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always increase indentation level"
msgstr "Alati suurendatakse treppimistaset"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Tab; key always indents the current line by "
"the number of character positions specified in <guilabel>Indentation width</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Sisselülitamisel trepib klahv &Tab; aktiivset rida alati märkide võrra, mis "
"on määratud valikuga <guilabel>Treppimise laius</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase indentation level if in leading blank space"
msgstr "Treppimistaset suurendatakse viibimisel rida alustavas tühjas ruumis"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Tab; key either indents the current line or "
"advances to the next tab position. If the insertion point is at or before "
"the first non-space character in the line, or if there is a selection, the "
"current line is indented by the number of character positions specified in "
"<guilabel>Indentation width</guilabel>. If the insertion point is located "
"after the first non-space character in the line and there is no selection, "
"white space is inserted so that the next tab position is reached: if the "
"option <guilabel>Insert spaces instead of tabulators</guilabel> on the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> tab in the <guilabel>Editing</guilabel> page is "
"enabled, spaces are inserted; otherwise, a single tabulator is inserted."
msgstr ""
"Sisselülitamisel annab &Tab;-klahvi kasutamine reale taande või liigub "
"järgmisesse tabelduspositsiooni. Kui lisamispunkt asub rea esimese "
"mittetühimärgist märgi kohal või eespool või kui midagi on valitud, antakse "
"aktiivsele reale taane, mille määrab kindlaks valik <guilabel>Treppimine "
"laius</guilabel>. Kui lisamispunkt asub reas pärast esimest mittetühimärki "
"ja midagi pole valitud, lisatakse tühimärk, et jõuda järgmisele "
"tabelduskohale: kui lehekülje <guilabel>Redigeerimine</guilabel> kaardil "
"<guilabel>Üldine</guilabel> on märgitud valik <guilabel>Tabeldusmärgid "
"asendatakse tühikutega</guilabel>, lisatakse tühikud, vastasel juhul üks "
"tabeldusmärk."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:680
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto Completion"
msgstr "Automaatne lõpetamine"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:683 configuring.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>General</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Üldine</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable auto completion"
msgstr "Automaatse lõpetamise lubamine"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, a word completion box automatically pops up during typing "
"showing a list of text entries to complete the current text under the cursor."
msgstr ""
"Märkimise korral ilmub kirjutamise ajal automaatselt sõnalõpetuse hüpikkast, "
"mis näitab tekstikirjeid, millega saab lõpetada parajasti kirjutatavat "
"teksti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto select first completion entry"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, the first auto completion item is always preselected so you can "
"insert it with &Enter;. If you do not want such behavior, &eg; if you want "
"pressing &Enter; to only insert a newline, then disable this item."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimal word length to complete"
msgstr "Lõpetatava sõna minimaalne pikkus"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While typing text, the word completion searches for words in the document "
"starting with the already typed text. This option configures the minimal "
"amount of characters that are needed to make the word completion active and "
"pop up a completion box."
msgstr ""
"Teksti kirjutamise ajal otsib sõnalõpetus dokumendist sobivaid sõnu. Selle "
"valikuga saab määrata minimaalse tähtede arvu, mida on vaja sõnalõpetuse "
"aktiveerimiseks ja lõpetuskasti avamiseks."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove tail on complete"
msgstr "Lõpu eemaldamine lõpetamisel"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:716
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remove the tail of a previous word when the completion item is chosen from a "
"list."
msgstr "Eelmise sõna lõpu eemaldamine lõpetuselemendi valimisel nimekirjast."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyword completion"
msgstr "Võtmesõnade lõpetamine"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, the built-in autocompletion uses the keywords defined by the "
"syntax highlighting."
msgstr ""
"Märkimisel kasutab sisseehitatud automaatne lõpetamine võtmesõnu, mis on "
"defineeritud süntaksi esiletõstuga."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spellcheck"
msgstr "Õigekirja kontroll"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These configuration options are described in the documentation for the "
"&systemsettings; module <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/spellchecking\">Spell "
"Checker</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Neid seadistusvalikuid kirjeldatakse Süsteemi seadistuste mooduli <ulink url="
"\"help:/kcontrol/spellchecking\">Õigekirja kontroll</ulink> "
"dokumentatsioonis."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vi Input Mode"
msgstr "VI sisestusrežiim"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid "Let Vi commands override Kate shortcuts"
msgstr "VI käsud tühistavad Kate kiirklahvid"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selected, Vi commands will override &kappname;'s built-in commands. For "
"example: <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> will "
"redo, and override the standard action (showing the search and replace "
"dialog)."
msgstr ""
"Valimisel tühistavad Vi käsud &kappname; sisseehitatud käsud. Näide: "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>sooritab "
"toimingu uuesti ning tühistab standardtegevuse (otsimis- ja "
"asendamisdialoogi avamine)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:753
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display relative line numbers"
msgstr "Suhteliste reanumbrite näitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"if this is enabled, the current line always refers to line 0. Lines above "
"and below increase the line number relatively."
msgstr ""
"Märkimisel käsitletakse aktiivset rida alati reana 0. Üleval- ja allpool "
"olevate ridade numbrid vastavalt suurenevad."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key Mapping"
msgstr "Klahvide seostamine"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Key mapping is used to change the meaning of typed keys. This allows you to "
"move commands to other keys or make special keypresses for doing a series of "
"commands."
msgstr ""
"Klahvide seostamist kasutatakse vajutatavate klahvide tähenduse muutmiseks. "
"See võimaldab omistada teatavatele klahvidele kindlaid käske või anda "
"teatavate klahvide vajutamisega lausa terve rida käske."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "Näide:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F2</keycap> -> <userinput>I--</userinput> &Esc;"
msgstr "<keycap>F2</keycap> -> <userinput>I--</userinput> &Esc;"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will prepend <userinput>I--</userinput> to a line when pressing "
"<keycap>F2</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"See lisab rea ette <userinput>I--</userinput>, kui vajutada <keycap>F2</"
"keycap>."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open/Save"
msgstr "Avamine/Salvestamine"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Format"
msgstr "Faili vorming"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:796
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encoding"
msgstr "Kodeering"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This defines the standard encoding to use to open/save files, if not changed "
"in the open/save dialog or by using a command line option."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab määrata failide avamisel ja salvestamisel kasutatava standardse "
"kodeeringu, mida kasutatakse juhul, kui seda ei muudeta avamise/salvestamise "
"dialoogis või käsureavõtmega."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encoding Detection"
msgstr "Kodeeringu tuvastamine"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select an item from the drop down box, either to disable autodetection or "
"use <guilabel>Universal</guilabel> to enable autodetection for all "
"encodings. But as this may probably only detect utf-8/utf-16, selecting a "
"region will use custom heuristics for better results. If neither the "
"encoding chosen as standard above, nor the encoding specified in the open/"
"save dialog, nor the encoding specified on command line match the content of "
"the file, this detection will be run."
msgstr ""
"Rippmenüüst saab valida sobiva valiku, ka näiteks keelata automaatse "
"tuvastamise või siis valida <guilabel>Universaalne</guilabel>, mille korral "
"lülitatatakse automaatse tuvastamine sisse kõigi kodeeringute puhul. Aga et "
"see tuvastab tõenäoliselt ainult utf-8/utf-16 kodeeringu, võib olla "
"mõistlikum valida konkreetne piirkond. Kui faili sisuga ei klapi ei ülal "
"standardsena valitud kodeering, avamis-salvestamisdialoogis määratud "
"kodeering ega käsureal määratud kodeering, siis alustatakse selle "
"tuvastamist."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fallback Encoding"
msgstr "Varukodeering"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:819
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This defines the fallback encoding to try for opening files if neither "
#| "the encoding chosen as standard above, nor the encoding specified in the "
#| "open/ save dialog, nor the encoding specified on command line match the "
#| "content of the file. Before this is used, an attempt will be made to "
#| "determine the encoding to use by looking for a byte order marker at start "
#| "of file: if one is found, the right unicode encoding will be chosen; "
#| "otherwise encoding detection will run, if both fail fallback encoding "
#| "will be tried."
msgid ""
"This defines the fallback encoding to try for opening files if neither the "
"encoding chosen as standard above, nor the encoding specified in the open/ "
"save dialog, nor the encoding specified on command line match the content of "
"the file. Before this is used, an attempt will be made to determine the "
"encoding to use by looking for a byte order mark at start of file: if one is "
"found, the right unicode encoding will be chosen; otherwise encoding "
"detection will run, if both fail fallback encoding will be tried."
msgstr ""
"See määrab varukodeeringu, mida püütakse kasutada failide avamisel, kui ülal "
"standardsena valitud kodeering, avamise või salvestamise dialoogis määratud "
"kodeering ega käsureavõtmega määratud kodeering ei sobi faili sisuga. Enne "
"selle kasutamist püütakse kodeering määrata faili algusest baidijärjestuse "
"tähist otsides: kui see leitakse, valitakse õige Unicode'i kodeering, "
"vastasel juhul käivitatakse tuvastamine ja alles kõige lõpuks kasutatakse "
"varukodeeringut."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid "End of line"
msgstr "Rea lõpp"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose your preferred end of line mode for your active document. You have "
"the choice between &UNIX;, DOS/&Windows; or Macintosh."
msgstr ""
"See määrab aktiivse dokumendi eelistatud rea lõpu režiimi. Võimalikud "
"valikud on &UNIX;, DOS/&Windows; või Macintosh."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic end of line detection"
msgstr "Automaatne rea lõpu tuvastamine"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this if you want the editor to autodetect the end of line type. The "
"first found end of line type will be used for the whole file."
msgstr ""
"Märkimisel tuvastab redaktor ise automaatselt rea lõpu tüübi. Esimest leitud "
"rea lõpu tüüpi kasutatakse terves failis."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:845
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Enable byte order marker"
msgid "Enable byte order mark (BOM)"
msgstr "Baidijärjestuse tähiste lubamine"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:847
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The byte order mark is a special sequence at the beginning of unicode "
#| "encoded documents. It helps editors to open text documents with the "
#| "correct unicode encoding. For more information see <ulink url=\"http://en."
#| "wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte_Order_Mark\">Byte Order Mark</ulink>."
msgid ""
"The byte order mark is a special sequence at the beginning of unicode "
"encoded documents. It helps editors to open text documents with the correct "
"unicode encoding. For more information see <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Byte_order_mark\">Byte Order Mark</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Baidijärjestuse tähis on spetsiaalne jada Unicode'i kodeeringus dokumentide "
"alguses. See aitab redaktoril avada tekstidokumendid õiges Unicode'i "
"kodeeringus. Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Byte_Order_Mark\">Byte Order Mark</ulink> (inglise keeles)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line Length Limit"
msgstr "Reapikkuse piirang"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, due to deficiencies in &Qt;, &kappname; experiences poor "
"performance when working with extremely long lines. For that reason, "
"&kappname; will automatically wrap lines when they are longer than the "
"number of characters specified here. To disable this, set this to "
"<userinput>0</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Paraku ei ole &Qt; puudujääkide tõttu &kappname; just kõige parem tööriist, "
"kui asi puudutab eriti pikki ridu. Seepärast murrab &kappname; read "
"automaatselt, kui nad on pikemad kui siin määratud märkide arv. Kui sa ei "
"soovi seda, määra väärtuseks <userinput>0</userinput>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Cleanups on Save"
msgstr "Automaatne puhastus salvestamisel"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:874
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove trailing spaces"
msgstr "Lõputühikud eemaldatakse"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:876
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The editor will automatically eliminate extra spaces at the ends of lines "
#| "of text while saving the file. You can select <guilabel>Never</guilabel> "
#| "to disable this functionality, <guilabel>On Modified Lines</guilabel> to "
#| "do so only on lines that you have modified since you last saved the "
#| "document, or <guilabel>In Entire Document</guilabel> to remove them "
#| "unconditionally from the entire document."
msgid ""
"The editor will automatically eliminate extra spaces at the ends of lines of "
"text while saving the file. You can select <guilabel>Never</guilabel> to "
"disable this functionality, <guilabel>On Modified Lines</guilabel> to do so "
"only on lines that you have modified since you last saved the document, or "
"<guilabel>In Entire Document</guilabel> to remove them unconditionally from "
"the entire document."
msgstr ""
"Redaktor kõrvaldab faili salvestamisel automaatselt lisatühikud tekstiridade "
"lõpust. Selle vältimiseks võid valida <guilabel>Mitte kunagi</guilabel>. "
"Valik <guilabel>Muudetud ridadel</guilabel> teeb seda ainult ridadel, mida "
"oled muutnud pärast dokumendi viimast salvestamist, <guilabel>Kogu "
"dokumendis</guilabel> eemaldab tühikud aga tingimusteta kogu dokumendist."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid "Append newline at end of file on save"
msgstr "Reavahetuse lisamine faili lõppu salvestamisel"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will automatically append a newline to the end of the file if one "
"is not already present upon saving the file."
msgstr ""
"Redaktor lisab faili salvestamisel automaatselt faili lõppu reavahetuse, kui "
"seda seal veel ei ole."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:898
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable Auto Save (local files only)"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this if you want the editor to autosave documents while you are "
"working on them."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto save document when focus leaves the editor"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will automatically save documents when you switch to something "
"outside the editor, &eg;, the terminal panel in &kate;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto save interval"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can determine the autosave interval in seconds here. If the interval is "
"0, the document will not be autosaved after intervals."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:927
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:931
#, no-c-format
msgid "Write a backup file on save for"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:932
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Backing up on save will cause &kappname; to copy the disk file to &lt;"
#| "prefix&gt;&lt;filename&gt;&lt;suffix&gt; before saving changes. The "
#| "suffix defaults to <emphasis role=\"bold\">~</emphasis> and prefix is "
#| "empty by default."
msgid ""
"Backing up on save will cause &kappname; to copy the disk file (the "
"previously saved version of the file) to &lt;prefix&gt;&lt;filename&gt;&lt;"
"suffix&gt; before saving the new changes. A backup file can help you recover "
"work if something goes wrong while saving or if you later want to recover "
"the previous version of the file. The suffix defaults to <emphasis role="
"\"bold\">~</emphasis> and prefix is empty by default."
msgstr ""
"Salvestamise ajal varukoopia loomise kasutamisel kopeerib &kappname; selle "
"enne muudatuste salvestamist kettale, andes failile nime &lt;prefiks&gt;&lt;"
"failinimi&gt;&lt;sufiks&gt;. Sufiks on vaikimisi <emphasis role=\"bold\">~</"
"emphasis> ning prefiks vaikimisi puudub."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:940
#, no-c-format
msgid "Local files"
msgstr "Kohalikest failidest"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this if you want backups of local files when saving."
msgstr "Märkimisel tehakse salvestamisel varukoopia kohalikest failidest."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:947
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remote files"
msgstr "Võrgufailidest"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this if you want backups of remote files when saving."
msgstr "Märkimisel tehakse salvestamisel varukoopia võrgufailidest."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prefix for backup files"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:955
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the prefix to prepend to the backup file names."
msgstr "Varundatud failide nime ette lisatav prefiks."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suffix for backup files"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:961
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the suffix to add to the backup file names."
msgstr "Varundatud failide nime järele lisatav sufiks."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:965
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Swap file options"
msgid "Swap file mode"
msgstr "Saalefaili valikud"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:967
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; is able to recover (most of) what was written after last save "
#| "in case of a crash or power failure. A swap file (.swp.&lt;filename&gt;) "
#| "is created after the first editing action on a document. If the user "
#| "doesn’t save the changes and &kappname; crashes, the swap file remains on "
#| "the disk. When opening a file, &kappname; checks if there is a swap file "
#| "for the document and if it is, it asks the user whether he wants to "
#| "recover the lost data or not. The user has the possibility to view the "
#| "differences between the original file and the recovered one, too. The "
#| "swap file is deleted after every save and on normal exit."
msgid ""
"&kappname; is able to recover (most) unsaved work in the case of a crash or "
"power failure. A swap file (.&lt;filename&gt;.kate-swp) is created when a "
"document is edited. If the user doesn’t save the changes and &kappname; "
"crashes, the swap file remains on the disk. When opening a file, &kappname; "
"checks if there is a swap file for the document and if it is, it asks the "
"user whether he wants to recover the lost data or not. The user has the "
"possibility to view the differences between the original file and the "
"recovered one, too. The swap file is deleted after every save and on normal "
"exit."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; võib taastada (enamiku) teksti, mis on kirjutatud pärast viimast "
"salvestamist, kui rakendust peaks tabama krahh või näiteks vool ära minema. "
"Pärast dokumendi esimest muutmistoimingut luuakse saalefail (swp.&lt;"
"failinimi&gt;). Kui kasutaja ei salvesta muudatusi ning &kappname;t tabab "
"krahh, jääb saalefail kettale alles. Faili avades kontrollib &kappname;, kas "
"antud dokumendile on olemas saalefail ja kui on, pärib kasutaja käest, kas "
"kaotatud andmed taastada või mitte. Kasutajal on võimalik eelnevalt ka "
"uurida erinevusi algse faili ja taastatud faili vahel. Saalefail "
"kustutatakse pärast igat salvestamist ja normaalse väljumise korral."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:975
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; syncs the swap files on the disk every 15 seconds, but only if "
"they have changed since the last sync. The user can disable the swap files "
"syncing if he wants, by selecting <guilabel>Disable</guilabel>, but this can "
"lead to more data loss."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; sünkroonib kettal asuvaid saalefaile iga 15 sekundi järel, aga "
"ainult sel juhul, kui need on pärast viimast sünkroonimist muutunud. "
"Kasutaja võib soovi korral saalefailide sünkroonimise keelata, märkides "
"valiku <guilabel>Keelatud</guilabel>, kuid see võib kaasa tuua suurema "
"andmekao."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the swap file is enabled, it is possible to switch between two modes, "
"namely <guilabel>Enabled, Store in Default Directory</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Enabled, Store in Custom Directory</guilabel>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:984
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Swap file options"
msgid "Store swap files in"
msgstr "Saalefaili valikud"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:985
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When enabled, the swap files are saved in the same folder as the file. "
#| "When <guilabel>Alternative Folder</guilabel> is chosen, swap files are "
#| "created in the specified folder. This is useful for network file systems "
#| "to avoid unnecessary network traffic."
msgid ""
"By default, the swap files are saved in the same folder as the file. When "
